  m_text: "GRAVITY SHIFT\nGI204 \xB7 Game Physics Project \xB7 2568\n\nDevelopment_team
    \n\nID: 1640706618\nSoravit Saeheng\nProgramming \xB7 Physics System \xB7 Level
    Design\nSection 229C | soravit.saeh@bumail.net\n\nID: 1640704514\nSomphong Phongphet\n\xB7
    Silde Presentation \xB7\nSection 229C | somphong.phon@bumail.net\n\nphysics_systems_used
    \n\nA\nUnity Physics 3D \u2014 Collision & Trigger\nOnCollisionEnter \xB7 OnTriggerEnter\n\n
    \u2014 Physic Materials\nDynamic Friction \xB7 Static Friction\n\nC\nNewton law
    2\nF = m \xB7 a\n\nE\nAir resistance\nF_drag = \xBD \xB7 Cd \xB7 \u03C1 \xB7
    A \xB7 v\xB2\n\nassets_&_tools ( Assets)\n\nAIRIDev Sci-Fi UI Icon Pack (Unity
    Asset Store \xB7 Free)\nPoly Planets (Unity Asset Store \xB7 Free)\nRocket (Cartoon,
    Capsule) (Unity Asset Store \xB7 Free)\nSci-fi GUI Skin (Unity Asset Store \xB7
    Free)\nStarfield Skybox (Unity Asset Store \xB7 Free)\n3D Models (Meshy.ai \xB7
